## Workflow After Each Edit (MANDATORY)
1. Build **prod APK** only: `flutter build apk --release --flavor prod --dart-define=INSTAGOLD_FLAVOR=prod`
2. Build **prod AAB**: `flutter build appbundle --release --flavor prod --dart-define=INSTAGOLD_FLAVOR=prod`
3. Copy outputs: `InstaGold.apk` and `InstaGold.aab` to repo root
4. Install APK on emulator: `adb install -r` (uninstall first if signature mismatch)
5. Launch on emulator: `adb shell monkey -p com.ibrahym.goldfamily -c android.intent.category.LAUNCHER 1`
6. Git commit & push
7. **Do NOT** build dev APK unless user explicitly asks to include dev
8. **Do NOT** upload AAB after each change — just build it
9. Upload APK to Google Drive (`rclone copy ... gdrive:InstaGold/`) only when user asks

## Settings Persistence
- Uses `shared_preferences` to cache theme (dark/light) and locale (en/ar) at app level
- On change: `SharedPreferences` is updated immediately in `_handleThemeChanged` / `_handleLocaleChanged` in `app.dart`
- On startup: `_loadPersistedSettings()` reads from SharedPreferences before showing any screen
- Also persisted to SQLite `UserSettings` table via `apiService.updateSettings()`

## Login Screen
- Always uses dark premium background regardless of theme (`PremiumBackground(forceDark: true)`)
- Gold gradient login button, gold-bordered input fields, top gradient header
- Matches the premium luxury dark theme reference design

